query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('cycles',
'organic-chemistry',
'python')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('android',
'blender',
'chemistry',
'diy')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1 group by t1.name;
